text: The New Moscow () is a 1938 Soviet comedy movie directed by Aleksandr Medvedkin and Aleksandr Olenin.Киносубботники пройдут в Екатеринбурге в рамках фестиваля "ЧО" It stars Daniil Sagal, Nina Alisova, and Mariya Barabanova. == Actors == * Daniil Sagal as Alyosha * Nina Alisova as Zoya * Mariya Barabanova as Olya * Mariya Blyumental-Tamarina as Grandmother * Pavel Sukhanov as Fedya Utin == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1938 comedy movies Category:Soviet comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Aleksandr Medvedkin
title: The New Moscow
